Detailed Description

cvmx_pesc::_tlp_credits

PESC_TLP_CREDITS = PESC TLP Credits

Specifies the number of credits the PESC for use in moving TLPs. When this register is written the credit values are reset to the register value. A write to this register should take place BEFORE traffic flow starts.
